{
  "id": "5fcd6f063873650021405581",
  "title": "ダメな設計を運用でカバーしている例",
  "created": 1607298823,
  "updated": 1672671236,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5fcd6f063873650021405581",
      "text": "ダメな設計を運用でカバーしている例",
      "userId": "5fa258bdb102120024d43875",
      "created": 1607298823,
      "updated": 1607298841
    },
    {
      "id": "5fcd6f30d438750000f41e48",
      "text": "マナー徹底キャンペーンをやりだす",
      "userId": "5fa258bdb102120024d43875",
      "created": 1607298864,
      "updated": 1607298929
    },
    {
      "id": "5fcd6f19d438750000f41e45",
      "text": " [エスカレーター]片側問題",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1607298841,
      "updated": 1672668523
    },
    {
      "id": "5fcd6f2fd438750000f41e47",
      "text": " [横断歩道]で車が止まらない問題",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1607298863,
      "updated": 1672668525
    },
    {
      "id": "5fcdd66f055332000012aa48",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5d131fa66fe2890017055332",
      "created": 1607325295,
      "updated": 1607325295
    },
    {
      "id": "5fcdd6a6055332000012aa4a",
      "text": "　とりあえずチェックリストを作成",
      "userId": "5d131fa66fe2890017055332",
      "created": 1607325351,
      "updated": 1607325358
    },
    {
      "id": "5fcdd66f055332000012aa49",
      "text": "　　本質的な改善/改修を行わずチェックリストを作成し恒久対策（[ヨシ!]）",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1607325295,
      "updated": 1645367512
    },
    {
      "id": "5fce056e4bb2e20000ffdf4a",
      "text": "　　機械でできるものをダブルチェックしてヨシ！",
      "userId": "5e8944948a182900174bb2e2",
      "created": 1607337269,
      "updated": 1607337289
    },
    {
      "id": "5fcd6f89d4387500009d5d4f",
      "text": " [ダブルチェック]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1607298953,
      "updated": 1645366728
    },
    {
      "id": "62124d0d5b98c20000435529",
      "text": " 　ダブルチェックは意外に信頼性が低い",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1645366541,
      "updated": 1645366581
    },
    {
      "id": "621250545b98c2000042efe1",
      "text": " 　統計を取ってみたら考えられていたよりずっと信頼性が低かった（要出典）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1645367380,
      "updated": 1645367528
    },
    {
      "id": "6212509c5b98c2000042efe2",
      "text": " 　特に上司と部下でのダブルチェックはダメだった",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1645367452,
      "updated": 1645367549
    },
    {
      "id": "621251035b98c2000042efe3",
      "text": " 　　考えてみれば当たり前のことで、上司のチェック漏れは指摘しずらい",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1645367555,
      "updated": 1645367620
    },
    {
      "id": "62124d445b98c2000043552a",
      "text": " [トリプルチェック]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1645366596,
      "updated": 1645366940
    },
    {
      "id": "62124d5a5b98c2000043552b",
      "text": " 　ダブルチェックより、さらにダメ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1645366618,
      "updated": 1645366646
    },
    {
      "id": "62124d765b98c2000043552c",
      "text": " 　[責任の分散]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1645366647,
      "updated": 1645367375
    },
    {
      "id": "62124d005b98c20000435528",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1645366529,
      "updated": 1645366529
    },
    {
      "id": "5fcdf8a15b98c20000d02fd4",
      "text": " [デザインの敗北]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1607334050,
      "updated": 1607334076
    },
    {
      "id": "5fcdf8c95b98c20000d02fd5",
      "text": "  カバーしている[テプラ芸]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1607334089,
      "updated": 1607334113
    },
    {
      "id": "5fcd6f89d4387500009d5d4e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5fa258bdb102120024d43875",
      "created": 1607298953,
      "updated": 1607298953
    },
    {
      "id": "5fcee774d4387500002efb91",
      "text": " [命札]は良い設計かわからんが、効果はあると思う",
      "userId": "5fa258bdb102120024d43875",
      "created": 1607395189,
      "updated": 1607395245
    },
    {
      "id": "5fcee772d4387500002efb90",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5fa258bdb102120024d43875",
      "created": 1607395187,
      "updated": 1607395187
    },
    {
      "id": "5fcd6f8bd4387500009d5d51",
      "text": "[/hub/マナーや運用に依存していたものを、技術とデザインで置き換えたい]",
      "userId": "5fa258bdb102120024d43875",
      "created": 1607298956,
      "updated": 1607298956
    },
    {
      "id": "621248528ee92a0000514a43",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1645365331,
      "updated": 1645365331
    },
    {
      "id": "621248528ee92a0000514a44",
      "text": "#ダメな設計",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1645365331,
      "updated": 1645365334
    },
    {
      "id": "63b2e9a5b8bbfc00009c8d33",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1672669606,
      "updated": 1672669606
    },
    {
      "id": "63b2e9a8b8bbfc00009c8d34",
      "text": "このぺージはもっと[シェイク]したい[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1672669608,
      "updated": 1672669743
    },
    {
      "id": "63b2ea30b8bbfc00009c8d35",
      "text": "\tシェイクとは？(唐突)",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1672669745,
      "updated": 1672671207
    },
    {
      "id": "63b2ea43b8bbfc00009c8d37",
      "text": "\t\t元々[Tak.]さんの造語",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1672669764,
      "updated": 1672669814
    },
    {
      "id": "63b2ea9bb8bbfc00009c8d39",
      "text": "\t\t\thttps://note.com/takwordpiece/n/n25145ede2165",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1672669851,
      "updated": 1672669851
    },
    {
      "id": "63b2ea75b8bbfc00009c8d38",
      "text": "\t\t\tアウトライナーで文章を書くとき、トップダウン・ボトムアップを行き来しながら構造を作っていくこと",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1672669814,
      "updated": 1672669833
    },
    {
      "id": "63b2eaa9b8bbfc00009c8d3a",
      "text": "\t\t最近[はるひ.icon]は勝手にそれを借りてアイデアの拡散と収束、具体化と抽象化を短いスパンで書いて考えることをシェイクと言っていがち",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1672669865,
      "updated": 1672671236
    },
    {
      "id": "621248538ee92a0000514a45",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1645365331,
      "updated": 1645365331
    }
  ]
}